question_text: Write a program to create a binary tree.
Write a program to implement tree traversal.
Write a program to check whether a tree is full or complete.
Write a program to create a binary search tree.
Write a program to sort a given set of numbers using BST.
Write a program to find mirror image of a BST.
Write a program to implement a two way threaded binary tree.
Write a program to print adjacency list of a given graph.
Write a program to implement BFS algorithm.
Write a program to implement DFS algorithm.
